r 665 recently taught by marilyn marchello bautista all public policy courses advanced legal writing legislative drafting and analysis bayesian statistics and econometrics econometrics mathematical methods economic analysis of law land use law and public policy colloquium legal profession economics and management of pro bono practice legislation statistical inference in law related links axess coursework digital reserve sls registrar mostly cloudy 50 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
